# 02 : LoA-v13 GRAND-VISION — DATA-AXES
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# § I> sibling-of 00_THESIS.csl
# § I> data-locality-discipline : LOCAL ⊕ SUPABASE ⊕ VERCEL boundaries
# § I> CSSL-native ; ¬ marketing ; ¬ exhaustive-API-list
# § I> consent-as-OS encoded into-data-locality ; biometric-NEVER-egress

§ AXIOMS  ‼ inherit 00_THESIS § AXIOMS
  t∞: data-locality is-an-architectural-decision ¬ optimization-detail
       ≡ where-data-lives = who-can-see-it = consent-boundary
  t∞: cap-gated-egress ‼ ¬ default-egress
       ≡ DEFAULT-DENY ; explicit-NET_*-cap-required for any-outbound
  t∞: biometric-family ¬ leaves-device  ‼ structural
       ≡ Sensitive<Biometric|Gaze|Face|Body> ⇒ TelemetryEgress refuses

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

§ LOCAL  «file-system caches + transient-state»

  § WHAT-LIVES-HERE
    asset-blobs    : GLB/PNG/WAV (binary ≥ 1MB) cached in LRU
    .meta-sidecars : SHA256 + license + source-url + dimensions
    audit-rings    : telemetry-ring lock-free producer-consumer (cssl-telemetry)
    image-snapshots: ω-field saved-state (cssl-orthopersist §§ 18)
    config         : runtime-config-bundle ; per-installation salt
    JSONL-logs     : per-frame telemetry rotated-by-size + by-day

  § WHY-LOCAL
    ✓ blobs > 5MB ⇒ Supabase-blob-storage costs prohibitive
    ✓ per-frame-telemetry ⇒ network-write would dominate frame-budget
    ✓ user-sovereignty ⇒ raw-paths NEVER-egress (path-hash discipline §§ 22)
    ✓ replay-deterministic ⇒ bit-equal-snapshots local

  § DISCIPLINE
    LRU-eviction by-mtime + by-total-size-cap (configurable, default 8GB)
    .meta-sidecar required for-each-blob (orphans purged on next-startup)
    rotation : JSONL-logs daily + size-cap 100MB ; gzip-archived
    salt : per-installation ; BLAKE3-key for path-hash (§§ 22)

  § WHAT-NEVER-LIVES-LOCAL
    ✗ secret-keys plaintext (use OS-keychain via cssl-host-keychain)
    ✗ player-PII (name/email/IP — never collected without explicit-cap)

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

§ SUPABASE  «relational + RLS-protected ¬ blob-store»

  § TABLES
    assets         : (id, sha256, source_url, license, kind, dims_json,
                       embedding_pgvector, created_at)
                     ≡ search-index ¬ blob-store ; blob lives @ source-url
    scenes         : (id, owner, cssl_source_hash, created_at, parent_id)
                     ≡ saved-compositions ; cssl-source canonical-truth
    history        : (id, user, event_kind, event_data_json, ts)
                     ≡ telemetry-aggregated ; ¬ raw-frame-events
    companion_logs : (id, session_id, role, msg_hash, intent_class, ts)
                     ≡ DM/GM/Collaborator/Coder trace
                     ≡ ¬ raw-msg-text ; only-msg-hash + intent-class

  § RLS-DISCIPLINE
    ∀ table : Row-Level-Security enabled
    history + companion_logs : owner-only-read ; service-role for-writes-from-edge
    assets : public-read for community-discoverable ; owner-only-write
    scenes : public-read if owner-marks-shared ; owner-only-write

  § WHAT-NOT-IN-SUPABASE  ‼ load-bearing
    ✗ blobs > 5 MB (assets table stores URL ¬ blob)
    ✗ raw-frames or per-frame-telemetry (use local JSONL+rotate)
    ✗ Sensitive<biometric|gaze|face|body> values (banned-egress structural)
    ✗ raw-paths or PII-fields (path-hash + opaque-id only)

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

§ VERCEL  «pure-compute edge ¬ persistent-store»

  § ENDPOINTS  (path → role)
    /api/intent           : text → typed-intent classifier (stage-0 keyword + KAN)
    /api/asset/search     : Sketchfab/PolyHaven/Kenney search-proxy
                            ≡ keeps API-keys server-side ; client never-sees
    /api/neural3d         : neural-3D mesh-gen gateway (stub-stage-1 ; real-W4)
    /api/companion        : companion-proxy → remote-Claude (DM/GM only)
    /api/marketplace      : community-asset-listing + voting (W4)
    /api/multiplayer      : signaling for peer-to-peer scene-sharing (W4)

  § WHY-VERCEL
    ✓ stateless-compute ; scales-to-zero ; pay-per-invocation
    ✓ API-key-server-side discipline ; client never-holds-secret
    ✓ rate-limit + abuse-shield via Vercel-native middleware
    ✓ deploy-on-git-push ; CI-linked

  § WHAT-NEVER-ON-VERCEL
    ✗ persistent-state (use Supabase for durable, KV-Edge for ephemeral)
    ✗ blobs (proxy-only ; never-cache-blob-on-edge)
    ✗ Sensitive<biometric|gaze|face|body> processing (¬ leaves-device structural)

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

§ READ-WRITE-PRIVILEGE  «who-can-touch-what»

  § SOVEREIGN-CAP-LADDER
    ApockyRoot          : top-level Sovereign ; can-revoke-anything
    AnthropicAudit      : audit-only ; ¬ mutate ; for PRIME-DIRECTIVE oversight
    PlayerInstance      : user-scoped ; can-mutate-own-scenes + own-history
    PublicAnonymous     : read-only public-shared assets + scenes
    DEFAULT             : DENY-all-network ; opt-in-per-cap

  § CAP-GATED-NETWORK
    NET_HTTP_GET        : read-only fetch (cap : NetGetRead)
    NET_HTTP_POST       : write-class ; rate-limited (cap : NetPostWrite)
    NET_HTTPS_ONLY      : ‼ default ; no-plaintext-transport
    NET_LOCALHOST_ONLY  : dev-mode ; ¬ shipping
    NET_BIOMETRIC_REFUSED: structural ; ¬ override

  § CAP-INHERITANCE  per Σ-mask § SOVEREIGN-HANDLE
    cell-claimed-by-Sovereign-X ⇒ mutate requires act-as-Sovereign-X
    SIG0004 mismatch on-violation @ compile-time
    runtime double-check Phase-5 AGENCY-VERIFY (defense-in-depth)

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

§ DATA-FLOW-MATRIX  «source × destination × cap»

  ```text
                  | LOCAL | SUPABASE | VERCEL | EXTERNAL-FETCH
  ----------------+-------+----------+--------+----------------
  raw-blob        | ✓ LRU |    ✗     |   ✗    |  via Vercel-proxy + cap-gate
  blob-meta       | ✓     |  ✓ FK    |   ✗    |  ¬ direct
  asset-search    |   ◐   |  ✓ index | ✓ proxy|  Sketchfab/PolyHaven/Kenney
  scene-cssl      | ✓     |  ✓ source-hash | ¬ |  user→cloud sync (cap)
  intent-text     | ✓ JSONL |  ✗ (hash only) | ✓ classify | ¬
  biometric       | ✓ on-device-only | ✗ STRUCTURAL-BAN | ✗ STRUCTURAL-BAN | ✗
  audit-chain     | ✓     |  ◐ root-only | ¬ | ¬
  ```

